text: "23" is a hip-hop song by American record producer and rapper Mike Will Made It. It also features American musicians Wiz Khalifa, Miley Cyrus, and Juicy J. It was released on September 10, 2013 by Interscope Records. The song is set to a midtempo beat. The lyrics mention Air Jordan Sneakers and recreational drug abuse.https://www.spin.com/2013/09/miley-cyrus-drug-rap-23-mike-will- made-it-juicy-j-wiz-khalifa/ "23" recieved mixed reviews from music critics. They were prevalent through its production and Cyrus' rapping ability. It peaked at number 11 on the US Billboard Hot 100. A music video for the song was released on August 26, 2013. It was premiered on Vevo on September 24, 2013. ==References== Category:2013 songs Category:Hip hop songs Category:Miley Cyrus songs Category:Wiz Khalifa songs
